          "type": "article_content",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Tom and I agree on almost nothing when it comes to the house. He’s a “wipe as you go” type. I’m more of a “leave it till the weekend” person. He thinks one product can do everything. I thought you needed a bottle for every surface.</p><p>But this autumn, we’ve both found ourselves raving about the same thing: a simple, natural cleaning spray that’s completely changed the way we tackle our seasonal reset, and for once, we’re not arguing about it.</p>"
          }
        },
